{
  "version": "1",
  "description": "Factory mapping of expense categories to the 7 DSOP principles. Loaded by app.principles.mappings.PrincipleMapping.from_file. Overrides (per ADR-008) live in SQLite (not yet implemented) and are layered on top of this file at runtime.",
